title: Import of creamery butter in Canada 2019
summary: This graph shows the Import of creamery butter Canada ( by Tonnes ) in Canada during 2019 each Month .
The graph fluctuates erratically throughout the year .
However , there was sharp decline between January and March after which the graph rose again .
gold: The graph shows the production of creamery butter in tonnes in Canada during 2019 . Overall , the level of production is relatively stable from January to September . The maximum production happened in October and created a significant peak in production .
